              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/b470a6399635e18331542458f1dad94e_7824935275349883747.png",
                "id": "talent46455",
                "key": "剑雨",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "剑雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消2点伤害。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1</span>，耗尽时不弃置此牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段，如果可用次数已耗尽：</span>弃置此牌，以造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6825430405167251199.png",
                "id": "talent95045",
                "key": "兔兔伯爵",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/73a2f9790672a39cb2f9a87b5f09ed6b_5377057380128565807.png",
                "title": "兔兔伯爵"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_8741905362489405892.png",
                "id": "talent80157",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_731757786184037330.png",
